Package models

Class OfficerRegistration

java.lang.Object
models.OfficerRegistration
public class OfficerRegistration extends Object
Represents an officer's registration to be assigned to a specific BTO project. This class tracks the registration process from submission through approval/rejection. Officer registrations are created when HDB Officers express interest in working on a specific project and must be approved by Project Managers before the officer is assigned.
